<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Survey Results — Analytics Report</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Crimson+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --crimson:    #A51C30;
      --crimson-dk: #8B1526;
      --navy:       #1D1D1D;
      --charcoal:   #2C2C2C;
      --gray-dk:    #555;
      --gray-mid:   #888;
      --gray-lt:    #E8E8E8;
      --gray-bg:    #F7F7F7;
      --white:      #FFF;
      --gold:       #C9963A;
      --sh-sm:      0 2px 8px  rgba(0,0,0,.07);
      --sh-md:      0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
      --radius:     10px;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
                   'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: var(--gray-bg);
      color: var(--charcoal);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    .w {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-inline: 40px;
    }

    .top-bar {
      background: var(--navy);
      padding-block: 7px;
      font-size: .72rem;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
      color: #999;
    }
    .top-bar .w {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .site-header {
      background: var(--crimson);
      color: var(--white);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 200;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
    }
    .site-header .w {
      padding-block: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .shield {
      width: 42px; height: 42px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.30);
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .brand-name {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .03em;
    }
    .brand-sub {
      display: block;
      font-size: .67rem;
      opacity: .75;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .10em;
    }
    .hdr-meta {
      font-size: .82rem;
      opacity: .85;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(
        150deg, #7A1020 0%, var(--crimson) 55%, #C0283E 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 40px 40px 48px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(
        circle, rgba(255,255,255,.045) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 28px 28px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero .w { position: relative; }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1rem;
      opacity: .82;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto 28px;
    }

    .stat-row {
      display: inline-flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.18);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .stat-cell {
      padding: 16px 34px;
      text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
    }
    .stat-cell:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .sn {
      display: block;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .sl {
      display: block;
      font-size: .68rem;
      opacity: .70;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .10em;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .toc-bar {
      background: var(--white);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gray-lt);
      padding-block: 18px;
    }
    .toc-label {
      font-size: .70rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      color: var(--gray-mid);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .toc-pills {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .toc-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 5px 13px;
      background: var(--gray-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-lt);
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: .78rem;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      max-width: 260px;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
      white-space: nowrap;
      transition: background .18s, color .18s, border-color .18s;
    }
    .toc-pill:hover {
      background: var(--crimson);
      color: var(--white);
      border-color: var(--crimson);
    }
    .toc-num {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 18px; height: 18px;
      background: var(--crimson);
      color: var(--white);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: .65rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: background .18s;
    }
    .toc-pill:hover .toc-num {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.25);
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 28px 40px 100px;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      padding-bottom: 18px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--crimson);
    }
    .section-head h2 {
      font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--navy);
    }
    .count-badge {
      background: var(--crimson);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 3px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
    }

    .chart-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-lt);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--sh-sm);
      margin-bottom: 44px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: box-shadow .22s, transform .22s;
    }
    .chart-card:hover {
      box-shadow: var(--sh-md);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .card-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 20px 28px 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-lt);
      background: var(--white);
    }
    .q-num {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 34px; height: 34px;
      background: var(--crimson);
      color: var(--white);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: .82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .card-header h3 {
      font-size: .97rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--navy);
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 28px 28px 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--white);
    }
    .card-body img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .card-footer {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 28px;
      background: var(--gray-bg);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-lt);
      font-size: .76rem;
      color: var(--gray-mid);
    }
    .footer-tag {
      background: var(--gray-lt);
      color: var(--gray-dk);
      padding: 2px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: .70rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
    }

    .site-footer {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: #888;
      padding: 52px 40px 30px;
    }
    .footer-grid {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
      padding-bottom: 40px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .f-logo {
      font-family: 'Crimson Text', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: #ddd;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .f-desc {
      font-size: .80rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .f-col-title {
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      color: #bbb;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .f-col-list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: .80rem;
    }
    .footer-bottom {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: .72rem;
      color: #666;
    }

    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .hero h1    { font-size: 2.2rem; }
      .stat-cell  { padding: 12px 20px; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
      main { padding: 24px 20px 80px; }
      .w   { padding-inline: 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top-bar" role="banner">
  <div class="w">
    <span>Survey Analytics Platform</span>
    <span>Data Visualization Report</span>
  </div>
</div>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="w">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="shield" aria-hidden="true">H</div>
      <div>
        <span class="brand-name">Survey Analytics</span>
        <span class="brand-sub">Applicant Response Report</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hdr-meta">
      May 06, 2026
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero" aria-label="Report overview">
  <div class="w">
    <p class="eyebrow">Survey Results</p>
    <h1>Applicant Response<br>Analysis</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      A comprehensive visual breakdown of all survey responses
      collected from applicants.
    </p>
    <div class="stat-row" role="list" aria-label="Report statistics">
      <div class="stat-cell" role="listitem">
        <span class="sn">2</span>
        <span class="sl">Questions</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell" role="listitem">
        <span class="sn">56</span>
        <span class="sl">Total Responses</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-cell" role="listitem">
        <span class="sn">12</span>
        <span class="sl">Unique Answers</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<nav class="toc-bar" aria-label="Jump to question">
  <div class="w">
    <p class="toc-label">Jump to question</p>
    <div class="toc-pills">
      <a class="toc-pill" href="#q1"><span class="toc-num">1</span>How did you hear about this program?</a>
      <a class="toc-pill" href="#q2"><span class="toc-num">2</span>What is your top reason for applying for or enrolling in t…</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<main aria-label="Response charts">
  <div class="section-head">
    <h2>Response Charts</h2>
    <span class="count-badge">2 Charts</span>
  </div>
  
  <article class="chart-card" id="q1">
    <div class="card-header">
      <span class="q-num">1</span>
      <h3>How did you hear about this program?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,"
           alt="Response chart — question 1">
    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
      <span>56 responses recorded</span>
      <span class="footer-tag">Survey Data</span>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="chart-card" id="q2">
    <div class="card-header">
      <span class="q-num">2</span>
      <h3>What is your top reason for applying for or enrolling in this program?</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64,"
           alt="Response chart — question 2">
    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
      <span>56 responses recorded</span>
      <span class="footer-tag">Survey Data</span>
    </div>
  </article>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer" aria-label="Report footer">
  <div class="footer-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="f-logo">Survey Analytics</p>
      <p class="f-desc">
        Generated automatically from applicant survey data.
        Charts represent response frequency distributions across
        all submitted applications.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="f-col-title">Report Details</p>
      <ul class="f-col-list">
        <li>Questions: 2</li>
        <li>Total Responses: 56</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="f-col-title">Generated</p>
      <ul class="f-col-list">
        <li>May 06, 2026</li>
        <li>02:01 PM</li>
        <li>Google Colab</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <span>© 2026 Survey Analytics Report</span>
    <span>Python · Matplotlib · Pandas</span>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
